package created 16 June 2025

similar methods employed in joetoo since 2015

get_wan_ip.sh script uses speedtest to capture the IP address the router's WAN has received from our ISP

post_wan_ip.sh posts that IP address to the Dropbox folder of our Dropbox user

Dependencies thus include
    net-misc/dropbox
    app-misc/jq
    net-analyzer/speedtest-cli
